resources.string: Double taabta Si aad u Wake
Kuu ogolaanayaa aad in tooso ka qalab by double siyoodba on ka screen.

Kuu ogolaanayaa aad in xirmaan USB qalabka. Goorma shaqeysiin kale qalab la xiriira USB hawlaha, sida sida ADB iyo MTP, doono ma noqon la heli karo ilaa this waa naafada ah ama ka qalab waa rebooted. Ma aha oo dhan USB qalabka doono shaqeeyaan.
Korodh ka dareenka of ka taabto screen si taabtana awooddo noqon diiwaan gashan halka xiran gacmo gashi.
awood ka labaad sim kaarka Afyare. Tani waa in ma noqon shaqeysiin haddii waxaa waa a sim kaarka in ka labaad Afyare. (baahan yahay Reboot!)

Tani shuqullada ku dhowaad arrimaha la Snapchat, Instagram iyo kale video duubo apps. Isticmaalida ka google avc encoder halkii of ka HW avc encoder. Waxaad laga yaabaa u baahan in qeybtii labaad ka app ama qeybtii labaad ka qalab ka hor this goob qaadataa saamaynta. Tani laga yaabaa sidoo kale Jidka qaar ka mid ah video duubo apps ma in shaqeeyaan.
Test tijaabo tignoolaji shidma! (baahan yahay Reboot)
Ma aha taageereen by this qalab...
mahadsan aad oo dhan waayo, aad taageero!
